At a bash prompt:
    cd  Wordpress-Database-Migration-Tool
    chmod 700 install.sh
    ./install.sh

The Wordpress-Database-Migration-Tool directory must be accessible via Apache.

Then browse to http://your-server/Wordpress-Database-Migration-Tool/move-wordpress.php

or, run:
    php move-wordpress-cli.php

to run from the command line.


